verses.verse: A Psalm <WH4210> of David <WH1732>. Give <WH3051> unto the LORD <WH3068>, O ye mighty <WH1121> <WH410>, give <WH3051> unto the LORD <WH3068> glory <WH3519> and strength <WH5797>. ye mighty: Heb. ye sons of the mighty

Give <WH3051> unto the LORD <WH3068> the glory <WH3519> due unto his name <WH8034>; worship <WH7812> the LORD <WH3068> in the beauty <WH1927> of holiness <WH6944>. the glory: Heb. the honour of his name in: or, in his glorious sanctuary
The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> is upon the waters <WH4325>: the God <WH410> of glory <WH3519> thundereth <WH7481>: the LORD <WH3068> is upon many <WH7227> waters <WH4325>. many: or, great
The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> is powerful <WH3581>; the voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> is full of majesty <WH1926>. powerful: Heb. in power full: Heb. in majesty
The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> breaketh <WH7665> the cedars <WH730>; yea, the LORD <WH3068> breaketh <WH7665> the cedars <WH730> of Lebanon <WH3844>.
He maketh them also to skip <WH7540> like a calf <WH5695>; Lebanon <WH3844> and Sirion <WH8303> like a young <WH1121> unicorn <WH7214>.
The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> divideth <WH2672> the flames <WH3852> of fire <WH784>. divideth: Heb. cutteth out
The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> shaketh <WH2342> the wilderness <WH4057>; the LORD <WH3068> shaketh <WH2342> the wilderness <WH4057> of Kadesh <WH6946>.

The voice <WH6963> of the LORD <WH3068> maketh the hinds <WH355> to calve <WH2342>, and discovereth <WH2834> the forests <WH3295>: and in his temple <WH1964> doth every one speak <WH559> of his glory <WH3519>. to calve: or, to be in pain doth: or, every whit of it uttereth, etc
The LORD <WH3068> sitteth <WH3427> upon the flood <WH3999>; yea, the LORD <WH3068> sitteth <WH3427> King <WH4428> for ever <WH5769>.
The LORD <WH3068> will give <WH5414> strength <WH5797> unto his people <WH5971>; the LORD <WH3068> will bless <WH1288> his people <WH5971> with peace <WH7965>.
